query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci mi_idx n it2) NoMergeJoin(ci it2 mi_idx n mi) */ select min(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
min(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
min(t.title) AS movie_title
from name AS n
inner join cast_info AS ci
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm' AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(head writer)',
'(written by)',
'(story)',
'(story editor)')
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror',
'Action',
'Sci-Fi',
'Thriller',
'Crime',
'War')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id;
